mdElement.text: Currently supports only concat of other properties and literal strings. If you need more from your calculation, use xImplHint.

KV - key, value.
PO - predicate, object.
CR - capability, role.
Separate with comma. Use CSV escaping if either term contains comma.
If any of these needs to be determined dynamically (e.g., collection depends on content), use xImplHint
